and reasoning behind it.

316
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,200
I went.

317
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,830
I went.

318
00:18:14,830 --> 00:18:17,160
I didn't find Zhou Delong.

319
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,480
But now we have.

320
00:18:19,750 --> 00:18:20,640
And he's dead.

321
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:25,160
Zhou Delong lived next door to you

322
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,480
for such a long time.

323
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,480
