333
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,830
It's been 14 years.

334
00:18:45,830 --> 00:18:47,960
I've paid the price for my mistake.

335
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:49,590
Because of you, because of this case,

336
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:51,000
I took off my prosecutor's uniform.

337
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,270
I gave up my daughter to you.

338
00:18:52,270 --> 00:18:54,070
I started over as a lawyer.

339
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:54,920
You've never once asked

